A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmerican%20news%20agencies%20said%20Israel%20conducted%20the%20attacks%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20the%20Jewish%20state%20neither%20agreed%20nor%20denied%20carrying%20out%20the%20strikes.%20The%20explosions%20occurred%20a%20week%20after%20Iran%20launched%20a%20relentless%20drone%2C%20cruise%20and%20ballistic%20missile%20attack%20on%20Israel%2C%20its%20arch-rival%20in%20the%20region.%20The%20targeted%20strikes%20from%20Tehran%20were%20unprecedented%20and%20occurred%20after%20tensions%20reached%20their%20brim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2Flive%2F2024%2F04%2F20%2Fworld%2Fisrael-iran-gaza-war-news%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-middle-east-68866548%5C%22%3EBBC%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20analysed%20satellite%20images%20of%20the%20region%20that%20was%20struck%20by%20drones%20and%20a%20missile%2C%20reportedly%20launched%20from%20a%20warplane.%20The%20satellite%20images%20show%20a%20battery%20of%20the%20Russian-origin%20S-300%20Surface-Air%20anti-ballistic%20missile%20defence%20system%20positioned%20northeast%20of%20the%20Isafan%20International%20Airport.%20The%20satellite%20images%20show%20the%20S-300%20defence%20system%20located%20at%20the%20secret%20facility%20on%20April%2015.%20The%20latest%20image%20on%20Google%20Earth%20shows%20the%20place%20empty%2C%20with%20no%20traces%20of%20the%20S-300%20missile%20defence%20system%20present.%20The%20Natanz%20nuclear%20facility%20is%20located%20north%20of%20the%20site%20of%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20comprises%20several%20vehicles%20equipped%20with%20radar%2C%20distinctive%20missile%20launchers%20and%20other%20equipment%2C%20the%20BBC%20reported%20based%20on%20its%20analysis.%20The%20drones%20and%20missiles%20reportedly%20struck%20the%20system%2C%20implying%20that%20Israeli%20weapons%20managed%20to%20evade%20the%20Iranian%20air%20defence%20system%20and%20went%20undetec