20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EIn%20view%20of%20forecast%20of%20above%20normal%20temperatures%20%26amp%3B%20heat%20waves%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20Commission%20is%20holding%20a%20meeting%20with%20different%20stakeholders%20this%20morning.%20The%20meeting%20is%20discussing%20measures%20to%20mitigate%20risk.%20Officers%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FiMD%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40IMD%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20NDMA%20and%20MoHFW%20are%20attending%20the%20meeting.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FAwjtrBnNwX%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FAwjtrBnNwX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Spokesperson%20ECI%20(%40SpokespersonECI)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FSpokespersonECI%2Fstatus%2F1782294690458443836%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20threshold%20for%20a%20heatwave%20is%20met%20when%20the%20maximum%20temperature%20of%20a%20weather%20station%20reaches%20at%20least%2040%20degrees%20Celsius%20in%20the%20plains%2C%2037%20degrees%20in%20the%20coastal%20areas%2C%20and%2030%20degrees%20in%20the%20hilly%20regions%2C%20and%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20is%20at%20least%204.5%20notches.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20severe%20heatwave%20is%20declared%20if%20the%20departure%20from%20normal%20temperature%20exceeds%206.4%20notches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIMD%20is%20in%20continuous%20touch%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India.%20Along%20with%20seasonal%20forecasts%2C%20we%20are%20doing%20monthly%2C%20week-wise%20and%20everyday%20forecasts%20and%20giving%20them%20forecasts%20about%20heat%20waves%2C%20and%20humidity%20levels.%20We%20are%20providing%20the%20ECI%2C%20inputs%20and%20forecasts%20about%20the%20places%20where%20elections%20are%20going%20to%20be%20held%20in%20different%20phases%2C%26quot%3B%20Director%20General%20of%20Meteorology%20of%20the%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%20Mrutyunjay%20Mohapatra%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20April%2011%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20had%20chaired%20a%20meeting%20to%20review%20preparedness%20for%20the%20ensuing%20heat%20wave%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20weather%20office%20IMD%20had%20issued%20an%20updated%20Seasonal%20Outlook%20for%20the%20hot%20weather%20season%20(April%20to%20June)%202024%2C%20in%20which%20it%20said%2C%20above%20Normal%20maximum%20temperatures%20are%20likely%20over%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20especially%20with%20high%20probability%20over%20central%20India%20and%20western%20peninsular%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20phase%20will%20be%20held%20on%20April%2026%20and%20the%20remaining%20phases%20will%20be%20May%207%2C%20May%2013%2C%20May%2020%2C%20May%2025%20and%20June%201%20accordingly.%20The%20last%20general%20elections%20in%202019%20were%20also%20held%20in%20seven%20phases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20ANI)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713781620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F10rfhg58_cec-1200_625x300_22_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-holds-meeting-to-mitigate-risks-due-to-heatwave-5497221%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20forecast%20of%20above-normal%20temperatures%20and%20heat%20waves%20in%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20held%20a%20meeting%20on%20Monday%20with%20different%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20officials%20of%20the%20weather%20office.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-holds-meeting-to-mitigate-risks-due-to-heatwave-5497221%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-commission-holds-meeting-to-mitigate-risks-due-to-heatwave-5497221%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fele