-news%2Flok-sabha-elections-2024-pm-narendra-modi-invokes-manmohan-singhs-muslim-remark-to-jab-congress-party-rebuts-5492647%5C%22%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20alleged%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20Congress%20government%20had%20said%20Muslims%20have%20the%20first%20right%20on%20the%20country's%20wealth.%20The%20remarks%20have%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row%2C%20with%20one%20section%20criticising%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20using%20expressions%20such%20as%20%26quot%3Binfiltrators%26quot%3B%20for%20Muslims%2C%20and%20another%20section%20slamming%20Dr%20Singh%20over%20his%20alleged%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Did%20PM%20Modi%20Say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20was%20in%20Rajasthan's%20Banswara%20for%20a%20rally%20ahead%20of%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20due%20this%20Friday.%20In%20a%20scathing%20attack%20on%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20pointed%20to%20the%20Opposition%20party's%20manifesto.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20Congress%20has%20said%20in%20its%20manifesto%20is%20serious.%20It%20has%20said%20that%20if%20the%20Congress%20forms%20the%20government%2C%20everyone's%20property%20will%20be%20surveyed%2C%20it%20will%20calculate%20gold%20belonging%20to%20mothers%20and%20sisters%20and%20then%20redistribute%20it.%20They%20won't%20even%20spare%20your%20mangalsutra%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20now%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20grip%20of%20urban%20Naxals%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20you%20accept%20this%3F%20Does%20the%20government%20have%20a%20right%20to%20seize%20your%20property%3F%20Gold%20is%20not%20for%20show%20off%2C%20it%20is%20linked%20to%20women's%20self-respect.%20Her%20mangalsutra%20is%20linked%20to%20her%20dreams.%20You%20want%20to%20snatch%20it%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20that%20when%20the%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20under%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%2C%20it%20had%20said%20Muslims%20have%20the%20first%20right%20on%20the%20country's%20wealth.%20%26quot%3BThis%20means%20that%20they%20will%20gather%20this%20property%20and%20distribute%20it%20among%20people%20who%20have%20more%20children%2C%20among%20infiltrators.%20Will%20your%20hard-earned%20money%20be%20given%20to%20infiltrators%3F%20Do%20you%20accept%20this%3F%20The%20Congress%20manifesto%20is%20saying%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Manmohan%20Singh%20Had%20Said%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi's%20remarks%20sparked%20a%20massive%20uproar%20as%20Opposition%20leaders%20slammed%20him%20for%20his%20comments%20on%20the%20Muslim%20community.%20The%20BJP%20responded%20by%20sharing%20a%20clip%20from%20a%202006%20address%20of%20Dr%20Singh%20at%20a%20meeting%20of%20the%20National%20Development%20Council.%20%26quot%3BWe%20will%20have%20to%20devise%20innovative%20plans%20to%20ensure%20that%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20the%20Muslim%20minority%2C%20are%20empowered%20to%20share%20equitably%20in%20the%20fruits%20of%20development.%20They%20must%20have%20the%20first%20claim%20on%20our%20resources%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20is%20heard%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%2C%20which%20captures%20a%20short%20part%20of%20the%20whole%20address%2C%20had%20sparked%20a%20row%20back%20in%20December%202006%20and%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20Office%20had%20then%20responded%20with%20a%20clarification.%20A%20PMO%20press%20release%20titled%20%26quot%3BClarifications%20on%20PM's%20reference%20to%20%26quot%3BFirst%20Claim%20On%20Resources%26quot%3B%20and%20dated%20December%2010%2C%202006%20states%2C%20%26quot%3BThrough%20a%20deliberate%20and%20mischievous%20misinterpretation%20of%20what%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%20here%20yesterday%20at%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20National%20Development%20Council%2C%20on%20fiscal%20priorities%20of%20the%20government%2C%20an%20avoidable%20controversy%20has%20been%20generated.%20The%20Prime%20Minister's%20observations%20have%20also%20been%20quoted%20out%20of%20context%20in%20some%20sections%20of%20the%20electronic%20media%2C%20fuelling%20a%20baseless%20controversy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20release%20went%20on%20to%20share%20the%20full%20text%20of%20the%20paragraph%20in%20which%20the%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20spoke%20about%20minority%20empowerment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20believe%20our%20collective%20priorities%20are%20clear%3A%20agriculture%2C%20irrigation%20and%20water%20resources%2C%20health%2C%20education%2C%20critical%20investment%20in%20rural%20infrastructure%2C%20and%20the%20essential%20public%20investment%20needs%20of%20general%20infrastructure%2C%20along%20with%20programmes%20for%20the%20upliftment%20of%20SC%2FSTs%2C%20other%20backward%20classes%2C%20minorities%20and%20women%20and%20children.%20The%20component%20plans%20for%20Scheduled%20Castes%20and%20Scheduled%20Tribes%20will%20need%20to%20be%20revitalized.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20devise%20innovative%20plans%20to%20ensure%20that%20minorities%2C%20particularly%20the%20Muslim%20minority%2C%20are%20empowered%20to%20share%20equitably%20in%20the%20fruits%20of%20development.%20They%20must%20have%20the%20first%20claim%20on%20resources.%20The%20Centre%20has%20a%20myriad%20other%20responsibilities%20whose%20demands%20will%20have%20to%20be%20fitted%20within%20the%20over-all%20resource%20availability%2C%26quot%3B%20Dr%20Singh%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20seen%20from%20the%20above%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20reference%20to%20'first%20claim%20on%20resources'%20refers%20to%20all%20the%20'priority'%20areas%20listed%20above%2C%20including%20programmes%20for%20the%20upliftment%20of%20SCs%2C%20STs%2C%20OBCs%2C%20women%20and%20children%20and%20minorities%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PMO%20had%20clarified.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20may%20also%20be%20noted%20that%20these%20observations%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20were%20made%20after%20referring%20to%20the%20very%20good%20performance%20of%20the%20Indian%20economy%20in%20recent%20months%2C%20and%20the%20expectation%20that%20the%20economy%20would%20continue%20to%20do%20well%2C%20creating%20new%20income%20and%20employment%20opportunities%20for%20all%20sections%20of%20society.%20While%20better%20off%20sections%20of%20society%20will%20benefit%20from%20this%20process%2C%20it%20is%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20Government%20to%20pay%20special%20attention%20to%20the%20welfare%20of%20weaker%20and%20marginalized%20sections.%20The%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20said%20on%20several%20occasions%20that%20'India%20must%20shine%2C%20but%20shine%20for%20all'%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOpposition%20Hits%20Out%20At%20PM%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister's%20remarks%20have%20triggered%20a%20sharp%20response%20from%20Opposition%20leaders%2C%20who%20have%20described%20it%20as%20an%20attempt%20to%20shift%20the%20discourse%20from%20public%20interest%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongress%20leader%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20is%20%26quot%3Bscared%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20first%20round%20of%20polling%20and%20wants%20to%20mislead%20the%20people.%20%26quot%3BTrends%20have%20started%20coming%20in%20of%20the%20immense%20support%20for%20Congress's%20revolutionary%20manifesto.%20The%20country%20will%20vote%20on%20issues%2C%20livelihood%2C%20for%20family%20and%20the%20future.%20India%20will%20not%20be%20misled%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%2C%20a%20key%20member%20of%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20INDIA%2C%20criticised%20PM%20Modi%20over%20the%20speech.%20%26quot%3BNot%20only%20the%20country%20but%20the%20whole%20world%20also%20knows%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20lies%2C%20the%20way%20how%20he%20spread%20lies%20about%20the%20Congress's%20'Nyay%20Patra'%20and%20former%20Prime%20Minister%20Dr%20Manmohan%20Singh%20is%20an%20example%20of%20dirty%20politics.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERJD%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20should%20talk%20about%20real%20issues.%20%26quot%3BWith%20folded%20hands%2C%20I%20appeal%20to%20him%20to%20quit%20politics%20of%20hate%20and%20talk%20about%20issues.%20The%20country's%20youngsters%2C%20the%20elderly%2C%20traders%2C%20farmers%2C%20the%20women%2C%20all%20sections%20have%20only%20one%20issue%20-%20poverty%2C%20inflation%2C%20unemployment%20and%20a%20poor%20economy.%20This%20is%20the%20real%20issue.%26quot%3B%20He%20added%20that%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20should%20speak%20on%20what%20his%20government%20has%20done%20in%2010%20years.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20is%20your%20vision%20for%20Bihar%20and%20the%20country.%20Instead%20of%20talking%20about%20that%2C%20only%20temple-mosque%20and%20Hindu-Muslim%20talk%20does%20not%20suit%20a%20Prime%20Minister.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESlamming%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20for%20his%20remarks%2C%20AIMIM%20chief%20and%20Hyderabad%20MP%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20posted%20on%20X%2C%20%26quot%3BModi%20today%20called%20Muslims%20infiltrators%20and%20people%20with%20many%20children.%20Since%202002%20till%20this%20day%2C%20the%20only%20Modi%20guarantee%20has%20been%20to%20abuse%20Muslims%20and%20get%20votes.%20If%20one%20is%20talking%20about%20the%20country's%20wealth%2C%20one%20should%20know%20that%20under%20Modi's%20rule%2C%20the%20first%20right%20to%20India's%20wealth%20has%20been%20of%20his%20wealthy%20friends.%201%25%20of%20Indians%20own%2040%25%20of%20the%20country's%20wealth.%20Common%20Hindus%20are%20made%20to%20fear%20Muslims%20while%20their%20wealth%20is%20being%20used%20to%20enrich%20others.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECountering%20the%20Opposition's%20charge%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20said%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20called%20a%20spade%20a%20spade%20and%20has%20echoed%20people's%20sentiments.%20BJP%20spokesperson%20Gaurav%20Bhatia%20told%20reporters%20that%20the%20opposition%20is%20in%20pain%20as%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20has%20showed%20them%20the%20mirror%20about%20its%20past.%20His%20remarks%20have%20resonated%20with%20people%20as%20for%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20those%20who%20have%20illegally%20entered%20the%20country%20%26quot%3Bare%20more%20important%20than%20citizens%20if%20they%20happen%20to%20be%20Muslims%26quot%3B%2C%20he%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Does%20Congress%20Manifesto%20Say%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20manifesto%2C%20which%20was%20targeted%20by%20PM%20Modi%2C%20calls%20for%20a%20nationwide%20socio-economic%20and%20caste%20Census%20to%20provide%20the%20data%20foundation%20for%20affirmative%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20Social%20Justice%20section%2C%20the%20manifesto%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BCongress%20has%20been%20the%20most%20vocal%20and%20active%20champion%20of%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20backward%20and%20oppressed%20classes%20and%20castes%20over%20the%20last%20seven%20decades.%20However%2C%20caste%20discrimination%20is%20still%20a%20reality.%20The%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20SC%2C%20ST%20and%20OBC%20communities%20have%20not%20yet%20been%20able%20to%20catch%20up%20with%20the%20rest%20and%20are%20still%20left%20behind.%20While%20OBC%2C%20SC%20and%20ST%20constitute%20nearly%2070%20per%20cent%20of%20India's%20population%2C%20their%20representation%20in%20high-ranking%20professions%2C%20services%20and%20businesses%20is%20disproportionately%20low.%20No%20progressive%20modern%20society%20should%20tolerate%20such%20inequality%20or%20discrimination%20based%20on%20ancestry%20and%20the%20consequent%20denial%20of%20equal%20opportunity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20manifesto%20then%20says%20that%20if%20elected%2C%20the%20Congress%20will%20conduct%20a%20nationwide%20socio-economic%20and%20caste%20Census.%20%26quot%3BCongress%20will%20conduct%20a%20nation-wide%20Socio-Economic%20and%20Caste%20Census%20to%20enumerate%20the%20castes%20and%20sub-castes%20and%20their%20socio-economic%20conditions.%20Based%20on%20the%20data%2C%20we%20will%20strengthen%20the%20agenda%20for%20affirmative%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20promises%20include%20a%20Constitutional%20amendment%20to%20raise%20the%2050%20per%20cent%20ceiling%20on%20reservation%2C%20filling%20up%20vacant%20posts%20for%20candidates%20from%20reserved%20categories%2C%20enhancing%20institutional%20credit%20to%20SCs%20and%20STs%20for%20building%20homes%20and%20starting%20businesses%20and%20establishing%20an%20authority%20to%20monitor%20distribution%20of%20government%20land%20and%20surplus%20land%20to%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713775620000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F3hvvam1g_modi-banswara_625x300_22_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-manmohan-singh-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-jab-manmohan-singhs-2006-speech-a-huge-row-5495887%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Addressing%20a%20poll%20rally%20in%20Rajasthan%20yesterday%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20alleged%20that%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh-led%20Congress%20government%20had%20said%20Muslims%20have%20the%20first%20right%20on%20the%20country's%20wealth%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-manmohan-singh-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-jab-manmohan-singhs-2006-speech-a-huge-row-5495887%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-manmohan-singh-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-jab-manmohan-singhs-2006-speech-a-huge-row-5495887%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-manmohan-singh-pms-wealth-to-infiltrators-jab-manmohan-singhs-2006-speech-a-huge-row-5495887%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Africa's%20ANC%20loses%20Zuma%20party%20name%20b