%20KKR%20won%20the%20game%20by%20one%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20after%20the%20match%2C%20Faf%20opened%20up%20on%20Kohli's%20controversial%20dismissal.%20He%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20crazy.%20Rules%20are%20rules%2C%20Virat%20and%20myself%20in%20that%20space%20thought%20the%20ball%20was%20higher%20than%20his%20waist.%20You%20always%20find%20one%20team%20happy%20and%20the%20other%20not%20so%20with%20such%20decisions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713774480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F5i0mt1gg_virat-kohli-bcci_625x300_21_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fipl-2024%2Fnot-good-for-the-game-navjot-singh-sidhus-blunt-take-on-virat-kohlis-dismissal-vs-kkr-5491847%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20the%20third%20over%20of%20the%20RCB's%20223-run%20chase%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20ended%20up%20mishitting%20a%20full-toss%20from%20pacer%20Harshit%20Rana%2C%20who%20completed%20an%20easy%20caught%20and%20bowled%20dismissal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22By%202100%2C%20Some%20Destinations%20Will%20Lose%20Half%20Their%20Nice%20Weather%20Days%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESpring%20is%20officially%20underway%20in%20North%20America%20and%20Europe%2C%20and%20crowds%20have%20rushed%20to%20dine%20out%20on%20terraces%2C%20bike%20along%20flowery%20meadows%20and%20boat%20in%20parks.%20It's%20a%20window%20of%20pleasant%20weather%20that%20scientists%20predict%20will%20give%20way%20to%20another%20record-breaking%20scorcher%20of%20a%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20window%20feels%20short-lived%2C%20there's%20reason%20to%20believe%20it's%20growing%20-%20at%20least%20in%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%20the%20century%2C%20residents%20of%20northern%20countries%20will%20generally%20see%20sunny%2C%20springlike%20balm%20appear%20earlier%20in%20the%20winter.%20Conversely%2C%20those%20in%20the%20south-including%20equatorial%20regions%20and%20extending%20into%20Southern%20Europe%20and%20the%20US-will%20for%20the%20most%20part%20enjoy%20fewer%20days%20of%20temperate%20weather%20year-round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20concludes%20an%20innovative%20study%20out%20of%20Massachusetts%20Institute%20of%20Technology%2C%20published%20in%20the%20Journal%20of%20Climate%20in%20March%2C%20that%20predicts%20the%20long-term%20effects%20of%20climate%20change%20on%20specific%20destinations%20around%20the%20world.%20The%20research%20combines%20data%20from%2050%20climate%20models%20to%20chart%20the%20ways%20in%20which%20%26quot%3Boutdoor%20days%26quot%3B%20will%20be%20numbered%20in%20various%20destinations%20by%202100.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20term%20refers%20to%2024-hour%20windows%20in%20which%20temperatures%20are%20pleasant%20enough%20for%20most%20people%20to%20enjoy%20outdoor%20activities.%20(Winter%20sports%20don't%20count.)%20The%20implications%20are%20enormous%20for%20quality%20of%20life%2C%20travel%20and%20tourism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChanges%20in%20the%20number%20of%20outdoor%20days%20will%20impact%20directly%20how%20people%20around%20the%20world%20feel%20climate%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20MIT%20environmental%20engineering%20professor%20Elfatih%20Eltahir%2C%20who%20led%20the%20study%2C%20via%20email.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20clear%20winners%20and%20losers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussia%2C%20Canada%20and%20other%20Global%20North%20countries%20will%20get%20more%20outdoor%20days%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Yeonwoo%20Choi%2C%20a%20postdoctoral%20researcher%20at%20MIT%20and%20member%20of%20the%20research%20team.%20%26quot%3BOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20developing%20countries%20such%20as%20Ivory%20Coast%20will%20get%20fewer%20outdoor%20days%2C%20so%20there%20is%20a%20clear%20disparity%20between%20the%20Global%20North%20and%20the%20Global%20South.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study's%20findings%20align%20with%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change%20will%20be%20more%20pronounced%20in%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20despite%20its%20countries%20having%20contributed%20fewer%20manmade%20greenhouse%20gas%20emissions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20changes%20will%20affect%20residents%20in%20such%20destinations%20far%20more%20profoundly%20than%20visitors%2C%20it's%20worth%20considering%20how%20climate%20change%20will%20alter%20the%20places%20that%20tourists%20visit.%20It%20has%20implications%20for%20where%20people%20will%20go%20and%20when%20they%20will%20travel%2C%20as%20well%20as%20for%20the%20tourism%20economies%20of%20countries%20that%20rely%20on%20vacationers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20this%20in%20mind%2C%20we%20used%20MIT's%20data%20to%20create%20a%20scorecard%20showing%20how%20outdoor%20days%20will%20fluctuate%20in%20the%20world's%20most%20visited%20tourist%20destinations-a%20ranking%20produced%20most%20recently%20by%20UN%20Tourism%20in%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fo771oovo_climate-change_625x300_22_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExtending%20beyond%20these%20most-visited%20countries%2C%20certain%20trends%20remain%20true.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20greatest%20impacts%20are%20expected%20in%20tropical%20destinations.%20The%20Dominican%20Republic%2C%20with%20124%20fewer%20outdoor%20days%20by%202100%2C%20will%20see%20a%2050%25%20drop%20in%20temperate%20climate%20year-round.%20Mexico%2C%20India%2C%20Thailand%20and%20Egypt%2C%20all%20in%20the%20Northern%20Hemisphere%2C%20will%20experience%20similar%20reductions%2C%20losing%20from%2055%20to%2086%20outdoor%20days%20a%20year.%20The%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%20will%20suffer%2C%20too%3B%20it's%20expected%20to%20lose%2085%20days%20of%20good%20weather%20annually%2C%20not%20accounting%20for%20a%20possible%20uptick%20in%20the%20torrential%20rains%20that%20this%20month%20brought%20Dubai's%20airport%20to%20an%20unprecedented%20standstill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20contrast%2C%20France%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Germany%20and%20Austria%20will%20gain%20from%2018%20to%2060%20outdoor%20days%20by%202100.%20This%20will%20be%20largely%20be%20due%20to%20warmer%20winters-unwelcome%20news%20for%20the%20ski%20industry.%20In%20the%20Mediterranean%2C%20Greece%20is%20estimated%20to%20lose%20more%20than%2030%20outdoor%20days%20by%202100%20due%20to%20hot%20summer%20temperatures%20from%20May%20to%20September.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EO'Shannon%20Burns%2C%20sustainable%20tourism%20consultant%20and%20program%20manager%20at%20Cornell%20University's%20Center%20for%20Sustainable%20Global%20Enterprise%2C%20says%20this%20is%20the%20first%20time%20she%20has%20seen%20a%20study%20using%20outdoor%20days%20to%20highlight%20climate%20change%20impacts.%20%26quot%3BThis%20really%20drives%20home%20how%20deeply%20the%20travel%20sector%20is%20going%20to%20be%20affected%20by%20climate%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says-%26quot%3Band%20the%20importance%20of%20climate%20action-planning%20at%20the%20destination%20level.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWant%20to%20see%20how%20outdoor%20days%20will%20change%20in%20your%20state%20or%20country%3F%20Use%20this%20website%20to%20find%20out.%20Select%20%26quot%3BSSP1-2.6%26quot%3B%20for%20results%20that%20reflect%20a%20more%20optimistic%20climate%20change%20outlook%20and%20%26quot%3BSSP5-8.5%26quot%3B%20to%20explore%20a%20darker%20scenario.%20Customize%20the%20results%20further%20by%20using%20%26quot%3BVariable%26quot%3B%20to%20select%20the%20range%20of%20outdoor%20temperatures%20you%20find%20comfortable.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713773760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-09%2Foqb7od5_-climate-change-bloomberg_625x300_23_September_21.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.c