nth-amazon%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprevious%20years%E2%80%99%20questions%3C%2Fa%3E%20suffices%2C%20Samyak%20notes.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20question%20bank%20(of%20notes)%20has%20around%202%2C500%20questions%20that%20feature%20ad%20verbatim%2C%20with%20a%20few%20changes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%20This%20leaves%20a%20candidate%20with%20the%20fourth%20section%20on%20which%20they%20must%20spend%20adequate%20time.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20section%20is%20more%20challenging%20than%20the%20others%2C%E2%80%9D%20Samyak%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECoaching%20might%20not%20be%20your%20cup%20of%20tea%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamyak%20once%20harboured%20a%20dream%20to%20become%20an%20engineer.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20phase%20when%20he%20was%20preparing%20for%20the%20IIT%20exam%20that%20he%20attended%20coaching%20classes.%20However%2C%20he%20instantly%20knew%20this%20style%20of%20learning%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20suited%20to%20his%20temperament.%20Thus%2C%20when%20it%20came%20to%20the%20UPSC%20exam%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20study%20by%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20wanting%20to%20dissuade%20anyone%20from%20opting%20for%20coaching%2C%20Samyak%20emphasises%20it%20merely%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20his%20cup%20of%20tea.%20%E2%80%9CTo%20each%20his%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reiterates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAcing%20the%20final%20frontier%20%E2%80%94%20the%20personality%20test%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20part%20of%20the%20daunting%20UPSC%20exam%20%E2%80%94%20the%20interview%20round%20more%20famously%20known%20as%20the%20%E2%80%98%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281037%2Fhow-to-crack-upsc-interview-tips-ias-officer-twitter-personality-test%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPersonality%20Test%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%94%20is%20actually%20designed%20to%20test%20one%E2%80%99s%20integrity%2C%20Samyak%20emphasises.%20Take%20its%20name%20seriously.%3C%2