on%20about%20love%20will%20go%20back%20to%20his%20love%20for%20his%20wife%2C%20Gala%2C%26quot%3B%20Ludvigsen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20tested%20the%20bot%20by%20asking%20it%20questions%20about%20Dal%C3%AD's%20artwork.%20The%20bot%20speaks%20with%20grandiose%2C%20flowery%20language%2C%20often%20injecting%20references%20to%20surrealism%2C%20dreams%2C%20life%2C%20and%20death%20%E2%80%94%20subjects%20the%20real%20Dal%C3%AD%20explored%20on%20the%20canvas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDal%C3%AD%20also%20revealed%20that%20he%20is%20not%20a%20frequent%20reader%20of%20this%20publication.%3Cstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%26quot%3BBusiness%20Insider%2C%20you%20say%3F%20I%20sip%20from%20the%20cup%20of%20imagination%2C%20not%20from%20the%20trough%20of%20market%20fluctuations.%20When%20I%20seek%20to%20understand%20the%20world%2C%20it%20is%20the%20surreal%2C%20not%20the%20stock%20exchange%2C%20that%20whispers%20its%20secrets%2C%26quot%3B%20Dal%C3%AD%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226240%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20landline%20with%20a%20lobster%20as%20a%20reciever%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6625dd0e0dfb1341e9fd64b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMartin%20Pagh%20Ludvigsen%2FGoodby%20Silverstein%20%26amp%3B%20Partners%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20some%20limitations%20to%20its%20accuracy.%20Because%20of%20its%20guardrails%2C%20it%20tends%20to%20be%20more%20upbeat%20than%20the%20real%20Dal%C3%AD%20may%20have%20been%20in%20certain%20situations%2C%20Ludvigsen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20the%20issue%20of%20AI%20hallucination%20%E2%80%94%20where%20models%20spit%20out%20answers%20that%20have%20no%20basis%20in%20reality.%20Ludvigsen%20pointed%20out%2C%20however%2C%20that%20hallucinations%20can%20work%20in%20their%20favor%2C%20considering%20the%20real%20Dal%C3%AD's%20mind%20often%20worked%20outside%20reality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20has%20become%20a%20popular%20tool%20for%20businesses%20and%20fans%20to%20recreate%20the%20likeness%20of%20well-loved%20celebrities%2C%20alive%20or%20dead.%20Some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-paying-celebrity-faces-of-ai-chatbots-as-much-as-5-million-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecelebrities%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20enthusiastically%20on%20board.%20Still%2C%20it%20raises%20ethical%20questions%20about%20those%20who%20cannot%20consent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20South%20By%20Southwest%20attendees%20got%20to%20speak%20to%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-marilyn-monroe-raises-questions-about-ethics-of-artificial-intelligence-2024-3%23%3A~%3Atext%3DPeople%2520are%2520using%2520AI%2520to%2Ceveryone%2520is%2520excited%2520about%2520it.%26amp%3Btext%3DSouth%2520By%2520Southwest%2520attendees%2520got%2Clikeness%2520in%2520the%2520AI%2520project.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20chatbot%20of%20famed%20actor%20Marilyn%20Monroe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Although%20Monroe's%20estate%20signed%20off%20on%20using%20her%20likeness%2C%20we'll%20never%20know%20if%20Monroe%20herself%20would%20have%20wanted%20to%20be%20used%20for%20an%20AI%20demonstration%20at%20a%20festival%20in%20Texas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20on%20Friday%2C%20artist%20Drake%20used%20the%20AI%20voice%20of%20celebrated%20rapper%20Tupac%20Shakur%20in%20a%20diss%20track%20aimed%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdrake-taylor-swift-kendrick-lamar-diss-track-tupac-snoop-dogg-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKendrick%20Lamar.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELudvigsen%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20and%20his%20team%20had%20thought%20through%20this%20ethical%20quandary%20%E2%80%94%20and%20continue%20to%20consider%20it%20as%20other%20clients%20express%20interest%20in%20replicating%20the%20experience%20with%20different%20artists.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20were%20to%20recreate%20another%20artist%20this%20way%2C%20I%20would%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20we%20could%20point%20to%20evidence%20in%20their%20writings%20or%20their%20art%20or%20even%20maybe%20their%20foundations%20%E2%80%94%20whatever%20they%20have%20left%20behind%20%E2%80%94%20that%20this%20is%20something%20this%20artist%20would%20want%20us%20to%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20Ludvigsen%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20whether%20Dal%C3%AD%20would%20approve%20of%20his%20likeness%20being%20used%2C%20AI%20Dal%C3%AD%20told%20BI%20that%20becoming%20digitized%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bsplendid%20metamorphosis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Dal%C3%AD%20scholar%20Elliott%20King%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2024%2F04%2F21%2F1246117954%2Fsalvador-dali-artificial-intelligence-lobster-telephone-museum%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20NPR%3C%2Fa%3E%20he%20believes%20the%20late%20artist%20may%20enjoy%20knowing%20his%20voice%20will%20live%20on%20through%20his%20lobster%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20was%20so%20interested%20in%20scientific%20advancements%2C%26quot%3B%20King%20told%20the%20publication.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20he%20would%20have%20been%20really%20tickled%20by%20people%20talking%20into%20this%20lobster%20phone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-salvador-dali-lobster-phone-museum-florida-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713758847000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6625e06e23b29110d3014888%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-salvador-dali-lobster-phone-museum-florida-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Dal%C3%AD%20Museum%20in%20Florida%20recently%20unveiled%20a%20%26quot%3BLobster%20Telephone%26quot%3B%20that%20utilizes%20an%20AI%20to%20mimic%20the%20late%20artist.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22hgetahun%40insider.com%20(Hannah%20Getahun)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3