ng%20Nigerian%20chess%20champion%20has%20played%20the%20game%20non-stop%20for%2060%20hours%20to%20break%20the%20world%20record.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fchess-champion-plays-for-marathon-58-hours-to-break-record-and-raise-cash-for-child-education-13119031%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews-sky-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fchess-champion-plays-for-marathon-58-hours-to-break-record-and-raise-cash-for-child-education-13119031%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fchess-champion-plays-for-marathon-58-hours-to-break-record-and-raise-cash-for-child-education-13119031%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Architect%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Beehive%E2%80%99%20Cooling%20System%20is%20Affordable%20%26amp%3B%20Reduces%20Electricity%20Bills%20by%2065%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20scorching%20summer%20heat%2C%20the%20demand%20for%20energy%20peaks%2C%20increasing%20our%20electricity%20bills.%20While%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F281434%2Fagra-data-scientist-builds-solar-power-eco-friendly-air-conditioner-exalta%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eair%20conditioners%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20artificial%20coolers%20not%20only%20drain%20our%20pockets%20but%20also%20harm%20the%20environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi-based%20Monish%20Siripurapu%20has%20come%20up%20with%20an%20affordable%20natural%20air%20cooler%20that%20not%20only%20keeps%20you%20cool%20in%20summer%20but%20also%20helps%20cut%20down%20on%20electricity%20bills%20by%20up%20to%2065%20percent!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20architect%20has%20designed%20CoolAnt%20which%20harnesses%20the%20power%20of%20nature%20to%20keep%20spaces%20cool%20and%20comfortable.%20Interestingly%2C%20its%20terracotta%20design%20is%20inspired%20by%20the%20efficient%20cooling%20techniques%20of%20beehives%20and%20brings%20together%20sustainability%20and%20functionality%20in%20one%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20system%20utilises%20terracotta%20cones%20arranged%20in%20a%20beehive%20pattern.%20Water%20is%20allowed%20to%20flow%20over%20the%20terracotta%20cones%20which%20acts%20as%20a%20natural%20cooling%20agent%2C%20absorbing%20heat%20from%20the%20surroundings.%20It%20then%20uses%20the%20process%20of%20evaporative%20cooling%20to%20release%20a%20gentle%2C%20refreshing%20breeze%20into%20the%20living%20spaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20the%20re-adaptation%20of%20traditional%20methods%2C%20combining%20ancient%20systems%20with%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F187517%2Flifestyle-eco-friendly-cooling-solution-without-ac-sustainable-homes-architect-india%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emodern%20technologies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20We%20are%20opening%20buildings%20to%20nature%20instead%20of%20building%20installations%20for%20conventional%20urban%20structures%20that%20shut%20their%20inhabitants%20into%20these%20closed%20boxes%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Monish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20startup%20observed%20that%20this%20structure%20can%20comfortably%20reduce%20the%20temperature%20up%20to%2030%20degrees%20Celsius.%20%E2%80%9CAt%20the%20factory%2C%20we%20reduced%20the%20temperature%20from%2045-47%20to%2032%20degrees%20Celsius%20because%20the%20water%20temperature%20was%2026-27%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%E2%80%9D%20informs%20Monish.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20CoolAnt%20was%20among%20the%2012%20winners%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20Low-Carbon%20Lifestyles%20Challenge.%20It%20bagged%20a%20%2410%2C000%20grant%20from%20the%20UN%20Environment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELearn%20how%20CoolAnt%20is%20helping%20homes%20and%20commercial%20establishments%20reduce%20their%20power%20load%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-as