pedal_n_66226f56e4b0167f7bf49593%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Accelerator%20pedal%20pads%20on%20the%20futuristic%2C%20all-electric%20vehicles%20have%20a%20risk%20of%20getting%20stuck%2C%20potentially%20causing%20them%20to%20crash%2C%20federal%20safety%20officials%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A136%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftesla-recalls-cybertruck-stuck-pedal_n_66226f56e4b0167f7bf49593%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-huffpost-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftesla-recalls-cybertruck-stuck-pedal_n_66226f56e4b0167f7bf49593%2Famp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Ftesla-recalls-cybertruck-stuck-pedal_n_66226f56e4b0167f7bf49593%2Famp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Startup%20Designing%20Indian%20Language%20Fonts%20for%20Apple%2C%20Google%20%26amp%3B%20300%20Others%20Makes%20%242%20Million%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20he%20was%20doing%20the%20lettering%20for%20the%20projects%20of%20classmates%20in%20boarding%20school%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20Satya%20Rajpurohit%20had%20no%20inkling%20that%20this%20skill%20would%20lead%20him%20to%20head%20a%20design%20firm%20that%20has%20developed%20450%20font%20families%20for%2020%20writing%20systems%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20enjoyed%20the%20creative%20process%20but%20did%20not%20yet%20understand%20that%20this%20was%20a%20fundamental%20aspect%20of%20type%20design.%20Later%2C%20I%20became%20fascinated%20with%20radium%20number%20plates%20for%20cars%20and%20bikes%2C%20which%20led%20me%20to%20experiment%20with%20custom%20letter%20shapes.%20I%E2%80%99d%20offer%20this%20service%20to%20my%20friends%20and%20family%20for%20free%20just%20so%20I%20could%20see%20my%20lettering%20being%20used.%20This%20was%20my%20unintended%20first%20step%20into%20public%20typography%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20unassuming%2040-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F98296%2Findian-type-foundry-satya-rajpurohit%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESatya%20co-founded%20Indian%20Type%20Foundry%3C%2Fa%3E%20(ITF)%20in%202009%20in%20Ahmedabad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20ITF%20with%20just%20one%20font%20family%20(Fedra%20Hindi).%20Since%20then%2C%20we%20have%20produced%20over%20450%20font%20families%2C%20including%20300%20retail%20font%20families%20available%20for%20licensing%20and%20around%20150%20custom%20and%20open-source%20fonts.%20Some%20of%20our%20most%20popular%20fonts%20are%20Kohinoor%2C%20Volte%2C%20Akhand%2C%20Poppins%2C%20Satoshi%2C%20General%20Sans%2C%20Swatzer%2C%20Teko%2C%20and%20Hind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETransforming%20typographic%20landscape%20with%20Indian%20languages%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20clocks%20an%20annual%20revenue%20of%20close%20to%20USD%202%20million%20(Rs%2016.48%20crore%20approximately)%20and%20has%20around%20300%20clients%20from%20Fortune%20500%20companies.%20Among%20its%20clients%20are%20giants%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20Apple%2C%20Google%2C%20Samsung%2C%20Sony%2C%20Amazon%2C%20Hyundai%2C%20Unilever%2C%20Tata%20Play%2C%20Star%20Sports%2C%20SBI%2C%20Zee%20TV%2C%20Mahindra%2C%20Disney%2C%20Kotak%2C%20Discovery%2C%20and%20Aaj%20Tak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%20Satya%20received%20the%20prestigious%20%E2%80%98SoTA%20Catalyst%20Award%E2%80%99%20presented%20by%20the%20Society%20of%20Typographic%20Aficionados.%20He%20has%20been%C2%A0featured%C2%A0in%20Fortune%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9840%20Under%2040%E2%80%99%20list%20for%20three%20consecutive%20years%20(2016%2C%202017%20and%202018).%20In%202017%2C%20he%20was%20also%20on%20GQ%20India%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9850%20Most%20Influential%20Young%20Indians%E2%80%99%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20ITF%20is%20recognised%20as%20one%20of%20the%20leading%20type%20foundries%20globally%2C%20having%20developed%20fonts%20for%20non-Indian%20languages%20%E2%80%94%20including%20Thai%2C%20Cyrillic%20(Russian)%2C%20Greek%2C%20Hebrew%2C%20Sinhalese%20and%20Korean.%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20what%20makes%20ITF%20special%20is%20its%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F45907%2Findian-languages-hindi-bengali-sanskrit-dravidian-kannada-malayalam-tamil-telugu-urdu%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efocus%20on%20Indian%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-500x500.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Akhand%20multiscript%20by%20ITF%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-500x500.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-300x300.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-150x150.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-768x768.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-1536x1536.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-2048x2048.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FAkhand-Multiscript_11zon-1713535979-96x96.jpg%2096w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347878%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAkhand%20multiscript%20by%20ITF%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20mission%20was%20to%20create%20a%20comprehensive%20collection%20of%20premium%20fonts%20for%20Indian%20languages%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20desire%20for%20cultural%20preservation%2C%20innovation%2C%20and%20addressing%20the%20needs%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20diverse%20linguistic%20heritage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satya.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20setting%20up%20of%20ITF%20was%20the%20result%20of%20a%20collaboration%20with%20a%20Dutch%20typographer%2C%20Peter%20Bilak.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeter%20offered%20him%20the%20chance%20to%20design%20a%20Devanagari%20(Hindi)%20font%20for%20his%20company.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20this%20font%20was%20complete%2C%20we%20searched%20for%20foundries%20that%20could%20publish%20it.%20However%2C%20there%20were%20no%20foundries%20in%20India%20at%20that%20time%20for%20Indian%20languages.%20This%20realisation%20prompted%20us%20to%20launch%20our%20own%20foundry%20with%20just%20one%20font%20in%20our%20library%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20relates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20secured%20Star%20Plus%20as%20one%20of%20its%20first%20clients%2C%20who%20licensed%20its%20first%20Hindi%20font.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBrahmos-1713536454-500x500.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brahmos%20font%20style%20by%20ITF%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBrahmos-1713536454-500x500.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBrahmos-1713536454-300x300.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBrahmos-1713536454-150x150.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBrahmos-1713536454-768x768.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBrahmos-1713536454-96x96.jpeg%2096w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FBrahmos-1713536454.jpeg%20794w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347888%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBrahmos%20font%20style%20by%20ITF%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vast%20linguistic%20diversity%20of%20India%2C%20with%20over%2011%20official%20writing%20systems%20and%20numerous%20languages%2C%20was%20largely%20underserved%20by%20the%20global%20typographic%20industry.%20Satya%20and%20Bilak%20noticed%20the%20lack%20of%20quality%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F139330%2Findian-street-fonts-art%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evariety%20in%20fonts%20available%20for%20Indic%20languages%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20compared%20to%20the%20extensive%20options%20for%20Latin%20scripts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20fonts%20for%20Indian%20languages%20is%20more%20challenging%20than%20doing%20so%20for%20world%20languages%2C%20says%20Satya%2C%20because%20Indian%20languages%2C%20unlike%20Latin%2C%20are%20complex%20to%20draw%20and%20have%20larger%20character%20sets%20that%20require%20several%20months%2C%20and%20sometimes%20even%20years%2C%20to%20design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20hard%20to%20find%20seasoned%20designers%20who%20are%20comfortable%20with%20both%20the%20language%20and%20the%20type%20design.%20The%20%E2%80%98matras%E2%80%99%20in%20Indian%20languages%20add%20to%20the%20complexity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98I%20cannot%20imagine%20a%20single%20day%20not%20thinking%20about%20fonts%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESatya%E2%80%99s%20parents%20wanted%20him%20to%20become%20a%20doctor%3B%20so%20he%20spent%20two%20years%20in%20Kota%20but%20failed%20to%20clear%20the%20exams.%20That%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20decided%20to%20pursue%20his%20interest%20in%20art%20instead.%20He%20joined%20Chandigarh%20College%20of%20Fine%20Arts%2C%20and%20while%20studying%20there%2C%20he%20learned%20about%20the%20National%20Institute%20of%20Design%20(NID)%2C%20Ahmedabad.%20He%20then%20secured%20admission%20to%20the%20prestigious%20design%20institute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20two%20years%20at%20Kota%20were%20the%20worst%20of%20my%20life.%20I%20was%20not%20a%20good%20student%20at%20school%20except%20in%20art.%20Even%20if%20I%20had%20cleared%20the%20medical%20exams%20and%20become%20a%20doctor%2C%20I%20would%20have%20been%20a%20terrible%20doctor%20because%20it%20was%20not%20something%20I%20wanted%20to%20be%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Satya%20with%20a%20rueful%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202407px)%20100vw%2C%202407px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222407%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Indic%20fonts%20by%20ITF%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047.jpg%202407w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-300x192.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-500x320.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-768x492.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-1536x984.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-2048x1312.jpg%202048w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIndic-fonts_11zon-1713536047-150x96.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347881%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221542%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIndic%20fonts%20by%20ITF%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20NID%2C%20he%20got%20interested%20in%20motion%20graphics%2C%20one%20application%20of%20which%20is%20creating%20titles%20and%20credits%20for%20films.%20However%2C%20here%20serendipity%20played%20a%20key%20role.%20He%20%E2%80%9Cstumbled%20upon%20an%20unexpected%20opportunity%E2%80%9D%20in%20his%20third%20year%20%E2%80%94%20an%20internship%20in%20type%20design%20at%20Linotype%2C%20the%20pioneer%20in%20making%20high-quality%20typefaces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThat%20experience%20was%20transformative.%20In%20those%20three%20months%2C%20I%20delved%20into%20the%20world%20of%20typography%2C%20gaining%20an%20understanding%20of%20its%20significance%20and%20intricacies.%20The%20experience%20ignited%20my%20passion%20for%20type%20design%20and%20reshaped%20my%20career%20trajectory%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Satya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20internships%20at%20Linotype%20in%20Germany%20and%20Dalton%20Maag%20in%20the%20UK%20were%20pivotal%20in%20preparing%20him%20to%20set%20up%20his%20own%20venture.%20They%20taught%20him%20the%20crucial%20blend%20of%20precision%20and%20creativity%20needed%20in%20type%20design.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20cannot%20imagine%20a%20single%20day%20not%20thinking%20about%20fonts.%20A%20font%20is%20a%20collection%20of%20letters%2C%20numbers%20and%20symbols%2C%20all%20dressed%20up%20in%20a%20certain%20style.%20When%20I%20design%20fonts%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20I%E2%80%99m%20designing%20outfits%20for%20words%20so%20they%20can%20express%20different%20emotions%20and%20ideas%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Satya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFonts%20have%20long-term%20value.%20For%20instance%2C%20Helvetica%20was%20first%20published%20in%201957%2C%20yet%20this%20font%20remains%20relevant%20even%20today.%20ITF%20develops%20both%20traditional%20fonts%20(used%20for%20text%20in%20books%20and%20newspapers)%20and%20experimental%20or%20display%20fonts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%