n%5C%22%3EAkshay%20studied%20using%20second%20hand%20books%20for%20competitive%20exams%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20father%20is%20a%20farmer%20and%20prioritised%20education%20for%20my%20siblings%2C%20cousins%20and%20me.%20He%20went%20above%20and%20beyond%20to%20provide%20us%20with%20the%20best%20education%20possible.%20After%20Class%205%2C%20I%20moved%20to%20Muzaffarpur%20to%20a%20better%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20Akshay%20tells%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20high%20school%20years%2C%20Akshay%20frequently%20resorted%20to%20purchasing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F280425%2Fsecond-hand-electric-car-ev-running-cost-in-india-range-battery-maintenance%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecond-hand%20books%3C%2Fa%3E%20due%20to%20the%20prohibitive%20cost%20of%20new%20ones.%20He%20vividly%20recalls%20instances%20where%20popular%20titles%20like%20R%20S%20Aggarwal%E2%80%99s%20Mathematics%20books%20or%20S%20Chand%20Publishers%E2%80%99%20textbooks%20for%20Class%209%20and%2010%20would%20be%20priced%20at%20over%20Rs%20500%20each.%20Fortunately%2C%20he%20managed%20to%20acquire%20them%20at%20a%20fraction%20of%20the%20original%20price%2C%20typically%20around%2050%20to%2060%20percent%20of%20the%20MRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20struggle%20continued%20when%20he%20embarked%20on%20his%20IIT-JEE%20coaching%20journey%2C%20necessitating%20visits%20to%20multiple%20shops%20in%20search%20of%20required%20books.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20wished%20there%20was%20an%20easier%20way%20to%20purchase%20these%20books%20and%20had%20noticed%20a%20huge%20demand-supply%20gap.%20So%20when%20I%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20get%20a%20good%20rank%20in%20JEE%20after%20two%20attempts%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20do%20something%20off%20the%20beaten%20path%20and%20try%20my%20hand%20at%20this%20business%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmed%2