Commission%20(UPSC)%20announced%20the%20result%20of%20the%20Civil%20Services%20Examination%20(CSE)%202023%20on%2016%20April.%20Thousands%20of%20aspirants%20looked%20for%20their%20names%20on%20the%20final%20list%2C%20and%20while%20the%20ones%20who%20found%20it%20rejoiced%2C%20the%20ones%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20felt%20dejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20cope%20with%20this%20dejection%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20Jitin%20Yadav%20shared%20a%20message%20of%20hope%20and%20how%20to%20handle%20failure%20on%20X.%20Titled%20%E2%80%9CFor%20the%20ones%20who%20did%20not%20make%20it%20to%20the%20final%20list%E2%80%9D%2C%20he%20gave%20his%20own%20example%20of%20what%20he%20did%20when%20he%20didn%E2%80%99t%20find%20his%20name%20on%20the%20%E2%80%9Choly%20pdf%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20message%20to%20everyone%20who%20didn%E2%80%99t%20make%20it%20is%3A%20%E2%80%9CDo%20not%20give%20up.%20Never.%20Be%20proud%20that%20you%20have%20come%20this%20far.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJitin%20recalls%20sitting%20in%20his%20Gurugram%20house%2C%20heart%20pounding%2C%20as%20he%20impatiently%20checked%20the%20UPSC%20website%20multiple%20times%20to%20see%20if%20the%20result%20was%20out.%20Finally%2C%20as%20the%20results%20were%20declared%2C%20he%20downloaded%20the%20million-dollar%20final%20list%20and%20checked%20it%20thrice%20for%20his%20name.%20He%20even%20did%20%E2%80%98Ctrl%20%2B%20F%E2%80%99%20with%20trembling%20hands%2C%20confirming%20that%20he%20hadn%E2%80%99t%20been%20selected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20numb%20and%20confused%2C%20and%20thought%20%E2%80%98Why%20only%20me%3F%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote%20in%20the%20candid%20post%20that%20now%20has%20over%201.25%20lakh%20views.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20friend%20who%20came%20to%20the%20bureaucrat%E2%80%99s%20rescue%20that%20day.%20Jitin%20met%20his%20friend%20and%20received%20an%20important%20life%20lesson%2C%20which%20applies%20to%20ev