20then%20struck%20him%20with%20a%20barrage%20of%20ground-and-pound%20strikes%20till%20the%20referee%20intervened%20at%20the%20end%20of%20Round%204.%20Following%20the%20fight%2C%20with%20the%20belt%20wrapped%20around%20his%20shoulder%2C%20he%20made%20an%20appeal%20to%20the%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20to%20restore%20peace%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20facing%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20heartfelt%20appeal%20went%20viral%2C%20the%20moment%20also%20marked%20Chungreng%E2%80%99s%20emergence%20as%20one%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20standout%20MMA%20fighters.%20When%20asked%20about%20the%20moment%20when%20he%20won%20the%20title%2C%20Chungreng%20says%20that%20he%20has%20no%20words%20to%20explain%20that%20feeling.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBrother%2C%20I%20worked%20so%20hard%20and%20overcame%20so%20much%20to%20be%20here%20now.%20Now%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%E2%80%99m%20finding%20my%20way%20in%20this%20sport.%20Although%20this%20win%20is%20a%20turning%20point%20in%20my%20life%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20only%20getting%20started.%20When%20I%20recently%20went%20back%20home%2C%20I%20was%20so%20happy%20and%20surprised%20to%20see%20people%20greet%20me%20at%20the%20airport.%20My%20village%20came%20out%20to%20celebrate%20my%20success.%20Watching%20all%20this%20really%20warmed%20my%20heart.%20Now%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20back%20in%20Delhi-NCR%20to%20help%20my%20teammates%20at%20Warrior%E2%80%99s%20Cove%20prepare%20for%20their%20fights%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%20fighter%20from%20the%20Koireng%20tribe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Koireng%20tribe%20is%20one%20of%20the%2033%20officially%20recognised%20indigenous%20communities%20of%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4fcJyhpSgl%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.