0Mumbai.%20He%20used%20to%20take%20his%20daughters%20there%20from%20time%20to%20time.%20Here%2C%20Hardika%20came%20across%20the%20courses%20taught%20in%20American%20colleges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20discovered%20liberal%20arts%2C%20where%20you%20can%20study%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20subjects%20and%20still%20get%20a%20graduate%20degree.%20It%20was%20just%20what%20I%20wanted%20and%20after%20I%20learnt%20about%20it%2C%20it%20became%20my%20goal%20to%20pursue%20this%20course%20in%20the%20US%2C%E2%80%9D%20Hardika%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardika%E2%80%99s%20upbringing%20was%20non-traditional%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways.%20Her%20mother%20had%20been%20ostracised%20by%20her%20family%20for%20her%20choice%20of%20partner%20and%20faced%20many%20struggles%2C%20yet%20the%20family%20chose%20to%20be%20happy%20and%20live%20a%20life%20full%20of%20love%2C%20happiness%20and%20dreams.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20her%20unconventional%20upbringing%2C%20her%20parents%20allowed%20her%20and%20her%20sister%20to%20dream%20big%2C%20work%20during%20junior%20college%2C%20have%20different%20life%20experiences%20and%20most%20importantly%2C%20go%20abroad%20for%20an%20undergraduate%20degree%2C%20which%20was%20quite%20unheard%20of%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHardika%20worked%20summers%20after%20finishing%20Class%2010%2C%20where%20her%20first%20job%20was%20working%20as%20a%20market%20researcher%20for%20shampoo%20fragrances.%20After%20that%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20font%20designer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CJust%20before%20going%20to%20college%2C%20I%20had%20to%20create%20fonts%20for%20Indian%20languages%20on%20the%20computer.%20Since%20they%20wanted%20someone%20who%20could%20handle%20computers%20and%20had%20an%20artistic%20mind%2C%20I%20got%20the%20job%20and%20worked%20there%20for%20three%20months%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F34